# device_smoke exercise: hold three keys in turn, capture each lit
# state, and let the boot jingle + key blips land in an audio dump.
# Frame numbers are emulator frames (bundled BIOS boots in ~60).
#
# Run: .\bin\gbarun.exe --rom test\device_smoke.gba --headless --frames 300 ^
#        --replay test\scripts\device-smoke.replay --dump-audio bin\smoke_audio.wav

100  press      A
110  screenshot bin/smoke_a.png
115  release    A
130  press      DOWN
140  screenshot bin/smoke_down.png
145  release    DOWN
160  press      START
170  screenshot bin/smoke_start.png
175  release    START
